-- Description:
--    LCD sample program for Microchip PIC 18f2320.
--    Shows some texts on a 2 x 16 LCD display.
--    Blinks also a LED on pin_A0 to show program is running.
--    Uses:  - LCD library lcd_hd44780_4.jal
--           - 4 LCD data lines
--           - DataPath: 4 individual bits
--
-- Sources:
--
-- Notes:
--  - File creation date/time: 14 Mar 2014 16:31:15
--  - This file is generated by script "lcd-sample.cmd"
--    and a table "lcd-sample.lst".  Do not change!
--
